        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Ques:- A Hollow shaft required to transmit 11.2 kW at a power of [UNCLEAR] at speed of 300 rpm. The maximum allowable shear stress 80 MPa and the ratio of inner diameter to outer diameter is 3/4."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Solution:- Given:"
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "P = 11.2 \\text{ kW} = 11.2 \\times 10^3 \\text{ W}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "N = 300 \\text{ rpm}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\tau = 80 \\times 10^6 \\text{ Pa}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Let $d_i$ and $d_o$ be inner and outer diameter respectively."
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\text{Then } \\frac{d_i}{d_o} = \\frac{3}{4}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "d_i = \\frac{3}{4}d_o",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "4d_i = 3d_o",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\frac{\\tau}{d_o/2} = \\frac{T}{J}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\frac{\\tau}{d_o/2} = \\frac{T}{\\frac{\\pi}{32}(d_o^4 - d_i^4)}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\frac{T}{\\frac{\\pi}{16}(d_o^4 - d_i^4)} = \\frac{\\tau}{d_o}",
          "display": true
        },
